{"tid":822892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳市已宣布山竹颱風來襲全市停工 香港工業傷亡權益會強烈譴責港府不立即跟進","createTime":"2018-09-16T14:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T14:57:08.000Z","uid":22349,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"19d5bc93c4c0ed18d7e428f13f0ff0f0435bdc0d","tid":822892,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:06:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1059482\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1059482&d=fuqJwH1o5lKpd4H2CyNvGtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=0aa2be51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1059482&h=3846aad5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1059482</a><br />\n<br />\n工業傷亡權益會<br />\n新聞稿：即時發布<br />\n深圳市已宣布全市停工　譴責港府不立即跟進<br />\n<br />\n和本港一水之隔的廣東省深圳市，因應強颱風山竹的危險程度，市政府城市管理局已經按照該局行之有效的《三防應急預案》，在今午六時宣布全市範圍停工、停業、停市、停課了。對比香港勞工處今午四時半的聲明，卻仍只是重申颱風及暴雨警告下的工作安排指引，提醒勞資雙方預早協商；這充分顯示香港特區政府缺乏停班完善機制，罔顧僱員生命安危。<br />\n<br />\n本會對此予以譴責，並重申因應強颱風山竹的危險程度，再次緊急呼籲：政府應即時宣布，除必要的應急服務外，在八號或以上風球訊號生效時，全港實施停工，確保市民停留在安全地方避風避災！<br />\n<br />\n在此，本會亦特別向香港天文台及其工作人員致敬！天文台是以科學為本的官方氣象觀測機構，並非主管勞工事務的政府部門，卻長期以來被迫承擔是否停班停課的政治責任。本會強烈要求勞工及福利局、勞工處均應負起上述政治責任，制訂妥善的惡劣天氣停工政策及機制。<br />\n<br />\n工業傷亡權益會<br />\n2018年9月15日"},{"pid":"53017526598cb72fa533bd19ade7f5b1b84c786c","tid":822892,"uid":102096,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:07:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8204ce6b6e361632d46002b9ca5c3791f543319","tid":822892,"uid":85659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:10:26.000Z","msg":"李氏力牆知道了<br />\n星期日吹夠十號爽不"},{"pid":"521e08f469c39942c3b8970ff6d8da66ef7a6ac0","tid":822892,"uid":22349,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:11:37.000Z","msg":"聽朝打工仔返工 <br />\n姐係今晚8號風球底下 迫地鐵火車復駛 迫住通宵維修好清理好條街同交通地鐵火車 <br />\n出面橫風橫雨又水浸又冧棚架 啲樹隨時倒塌<br />\n唔撚諗下 啲九巴港鐵工作人員同修路人員會有危險<br />\n屌你返工炸 揾命搏咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">修橋補路無屍骸</span></span>"},{"pid":"b30cd894eccdac1fc4419a67f279910358f0fbcd","tid":822892,"uid":132302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:12:24.000Z","msg":"早啲番工呀香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"6af7cad7fb8ee7268d3f027efaf8a9937490f5a0","tid":822892,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:12:55.000Z","msg":"自行停工"},{"pid":"69ebff28114f7c6e4dd9665b591bbbcea7ce209b","tid":822892,"uid":5289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:13:08.000Z","msg":"獅子山精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f8365a2f2e122d6ba8f0e1cec377307e9567f5","tid":822892,"uid":198223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/16/221317_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F16%2F221317_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=dd93bed2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab2a603b53e916a9d660912704da5b0db40ca259","tid":822892,"uid":22349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:24:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一般情況下，因上班途中或放工後不屬於工作期間，遇到意外不可視作工傷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"3362b467e32b329db757291ee544f4e2217fbf11","tid":822892,"uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:54:27.000Z","msg":"四級颶風佛羅倫絲吹襲美國, 東岸一百萬人撇離流離失所<br />\n超強颱風飛燕吹襲日本關西, 機場斷橋, 京都古蹟大崩壞, 日本人排隊飯團<br />\n超強颱風山竹吹襲關島, 街頭電纜短路起火, 美國派特別專機運送物資<br />\n超強颱風山竹吹襲菲律賓, 數百萬人受災, 菲律賓人入住臨時庇護中心<br />\n超強颱風山竹掠過台灣南部, 屏東局部停電, 墾丁捲起滔天巨浪<br />\n超強颱風山竹吹襲深圳, 政府發動「緊急動員令」, 全市停工停業停市停課<br />\n超強颱風山竹吹襲澳門, 澳門大範圍水浸, 澳門人撤出賭場, 翌日停工停學<br />\n超強颱風山竹吹襲香港, 香港人: <br />\n<br />\n&quot;打完風, 明天是時候準時返工了!&quot;"},{"pid":"a6d5e7777380636eda2e3f1fe3bf89dbf98c82db","tid":822892,"uid":162441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1274286/org/a7a09c994f7c0d9c05c5ac5e746f20e9.jpg/1-XQDn3YX0a9JtMU1C6cqck1vpZRug0Lh23u_Idt7vw?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1274286%2Forg%2Fa7a09c994f7c0d9c05c5ac5e746f20e9.jpg%2F1-XQDn3YX0a9JtMU1C6cqck1vpZRug0Lh23u_Idt7vw%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=8b159cf8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f9ac5b5da7b24be600e644b38664c6cf83d130c","tid":822892,"uid":17859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53017526598cb72fa533bd19ade7f5b1b84c786c","tid":822892,"uid":102096,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:07:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:57:08.000Z","msg":"你老母做少一日又唔見幾個恩客嘅錢<br />\n又唔夠錢養你件低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}